    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule: the leather remains supple and matte with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable, featuring a full service history with all scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by the dealership. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. Complete service records, original window sticker, and two sets of keys are included.",
      "price": 43900.0,
