    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered since day one. Honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single blemish to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and even still has that wonderful new car smell. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
