    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and retains its factory-spec suspension geometry with refreshed bushings. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits zero clear-coat failure or rock chips. Recent comprehensive service includes rod bearing replacement and a precision valve adjustment, ensuring this high-revving masterpiece performs at its peak. A truly turn-key, investment-quality icon.",
